  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>In the morning enjoy a buffet breakfast with a good choice of breads, jams, cold cuts and hot options. You can choose to dine inside or out on the terrace in good weather.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurant &amp; Pizzeria </strong>is an <span>à l</span>a carte restaurant overlooking Piazza Ill Novembre. Tables and chairs sprawl out across the square so you can dine al fresco. Come here in the early evening for aperitivo and stay for the pizzas, risottos and freshly caught fish from the lake. </p>
<p>Inside the main restaurant the food focusses on traditional Trentino and Italian dishes accompanied by a buffet of appetisers and salads. Guests staying at the Portici receive a 15% discount off the restaurant menu. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
