  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Portici is a lovely base for your stay in Riva. It's right in the historic centre and close to the ferry point, connecting you to other resorts on <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a>. The outdoor bar terrace in the piazza is a great spot for aperitivo. </p>]]></listingDescription>
