  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are about 18m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They're decorated in a modern style with wooden floors and furnishings. <span>Facilities include air conditioning (June to mid September), TV, safe, mini-fridge, shower and hairdryer.</span></p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are about 18m² and have lovely views across the piazza. </p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are about 12<span>m² and have a French bed.</span></p>]]></roomsDescription>
